Shank's Take:
The thief. The coward's profession. If you're gonna break established laws, DO IT IN STYLE! Hiding in the shadows, fighting exclusively for yourself, it's a show of weakness. A professional makes sure he's known!

Dagger's Take:
The thief, I HATE THEM! Not only did they beat me in a fight, they destroyed my sunglasses. I won't rest until I destroy something of theirs. Something precious to them.
